				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-72fcd1f wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="72fcd1f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">I began my career in <span class="hl-text">graphic design</span>, working as a freelancer for clients across the globe. This experience allowed me to develop a strong foundation in design while adapting to the diverse needs of international clients.

</br></br>

Driven by a desire to understand how software works, I taught myself to code and spent <span class="hl-text">+3 years as a full-stack developer</span> at a tech company. This role gave me valuable insights into the technical side of product creation, bridging the gap between design and development.

</br></br>

With this blend of skills, I decided to <span class="hl-text">create my own products</span>. I designed, developed and launched two apps in over 80 countries, achieving more than 3 million downloads and a rating of over 4 stars on Google Play.

</br></br>

As a result, I am now a design leader with <span class="hl-text">+10 years of hands-on experience</span>. My co-founder mentality drives me to solve problems with a strong product vision, ensuring that my work is always aligned with business strategy.
</p>				</div>
				</div>
