</ul>

<p class="num" style="font-size: 10pt !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #ffffff66 !important;margin-top: 24px !important;margin-bottom: 8px !important">*This was an entrepreneurship that failed due to a lack of business and operational knowledge.</p></div></div></div></div>
